%% Request/Response Flow - Complete Cycle
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant User as 👤 User Browser
    participant NextJS as ⚡ Next.js Server
    participant Router as 🛣️ App Router
    participant Component as ⚛️ React Component
    participant ServerAction as 🔧 Server Action
    participant Auth as 🔐 Better Auth
    participant DB as 💾 MongoDB
    participant External as 🌐 External APIs
    participant Inngest as ⏰ Inngest
    
    Note over User,Inngest: Page Load Request Flow
    
    User->>NextJS: HTTP GET /dashboard
    NextJS->>Router: Route to (root)/dashboard/page.tsx
    Router->>Auth: Check Session (getSession)
    Auth->>DB: Query User Collection
    DB-->>Auth: Return User Data
    Auth-->>Router: Session Status
    
    alt User Not Authenticated
        Router-->>NextJS: Redirect to /sign-in
        NextJS-->>User: 302 Redirect Response
    else User Authenticated
        Router->>Component: Render DashboardPage
        Component->>Component: Call useUserDashboardLayout(userId)
        Component->>ServerAction: getUserDashboardLayout(userId)
        ServerAction->>DB: Query UserPreferences Collection
        DB-->>ServerAction: Return Layout Data (or null)
        ServerAction-->>Component: Return Layout
        Component->>External: Load TradingView Widgets (iframe)
        External-->>Component: Render Widgets
        Component-->>Router: Rendered HTML/JSX
        Router-->>NextJS: Server Component Output
        NextJS-->>User: HTML Response + Hydration JS
    end
    
    Note over User,Inngest: User Interaction Flow (Example: Sign Up)
    
    User->>Component: Submit Sign Up Form
    Component->>ServerAction: signUpWithEmail(formData)
    ServerAction->>Auth: auth.api.signUpEmail()
    Auth->>DB: Create User Document
    DB-->>Auth: User Created
    Auth-->>ServerAction: User Response
    
    ServerAction->>ServerAction: saveUserPreferences(userId, prefs)
    ServerAction->>DB: Upsert UserPreferences Document
    DB-->>ServerAction: Preferences Saved
    
    ServerAction->>Inngest: inngest.send('app/user.created')
    Inngest-->>ServerAction: Event Queued
    
    ServerAction-->>Component: Return { success: true }
    Component->>Router: Redirect to /dashboard
    Router-->>NextJS: Navigation Response
    NextJS-->>User: Redirect Response
    
    Note over User,Inngest: Background Job Flow (Welcome Email)
    
    Inngest->>Inngest: Process 'app/user.created' Event
    Inngest->>External: Call Gemini AI (Generate Intro)
    External-->>Inngest: Personalized Content
    Inngest->>External: Send Email via Nodemailer
    External-->>Inngest: Email Sent Confirmation
    Inngest->>Inngest: Job Complete
    
    Note over User,Inngest: API Request Flow (Example: Add to Watchlist)
    
    User->>Component: Click "Add to Watchlist"
    Component->>ServerAction: addToWatchlist(symbol, company)
    ServerAction->>Auth: Get Current Session
    Auth->>DB: Verify User
    DB-->>Auth: User Valid
    Auth-->>ServerAction: User ID
    
    ServerAction->>DB: Insert Watchlist Document
    DB-->>ServerAction: Document Created
    ServerAction-->>Component: Return { success: true }
    Component->>Component: Update UI State
    Component-->>User: Show Success Message
    
    Note over User,Inngest: External API Request Flow (Example: Fetch News)
    
    User->>Component: Load Dashboard (with news widget)
    Component->>ServerAction: getNews(symbols)
    ServerAction->>External: GET https://finnhub.io/api/v1/news
    External-->>ServerAction: News Articles JSON
    ServerAction->>ServerAction: Validate & Format Articles
    ServerAction-->>Component: Return Formatted News
    Component->>Component: Render News Widget
    Component-->>User: Display News Content
